To install:

(Assuming kernel sources are in /usr/src/linux or /usr/src/linux-VERSION)

copy the whole directory to /usr/src/shall
cd /usr/src/linux (or linux-VERSION)
patch -sp1 < ../shall/install/shall.patch
sh ../shall/install/shall.script

make menuconfig
  File systems  --->
    Pseudo filesystems  --->
      <M> The shall filesystem
      [*]   shall filesystem debugging support

make
make install
make modules_install

Then "modprobe shallfs" (or just "mount -tshallfs" will autoload the module)

